cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.LG 

The paper discusses the design of an optimal reminder system to cope with prospective memory failures, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The proposed system also includes a personalized user model, which can be related to cybernetics (cs.CY) and social intelligence (cs.SI). Finally, the optimization of the reminder plan can be related to machine learning (cs.LG) techniques.
